      "side": 1,
      "message": "What do you think about using a statement-expression:\n\n```\nstatic pthread_key_t get_pthread_key() {\n    static pthread_key_t sKey \u003d ({\n       pthread_key_t tmpKey;\n       SkAssertResult(0 \u003d\u003d pthread_key_create(\u0026tmpKey, /*destructor\u003d*/nullptr));\n       tmpKey;\n    });\n    return sKey;\n}\n```",
      "revId": "9c7c40b4f71329f833d9bcb1eeb3d98c802caaf8",
