      "side": 1,
      "message": "Anyway, if I\u0027ve accidentally got your attention, what\u0027s your take on statement-expressions in Skia (in cases like this where MSVC compliance is a non-issue)? My gut feel is \"no\" but curious if I\u0027m misreading it.",
