      "writtenOn": "2020-10-21T14:35:29Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "(FWIW, now that I\u0027ve learned that the immediate-lambda pattern is zero-cost, it\u0027s the clear winner for being standard C++).",
      "parentUuid": "8d864357_4144fda2",
      "revId": "9c7c40b4f71329f833d9bcb1eeb3d98c802caaf8",
