      "writtenOn": "2020-10-21T15:17:35Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "If thread safety weren\u0027t an issue we wouldn\u0027t be doing any of this.\n\nIt\u0027s okay not to know things, but it\u0027s not productive to retroactively argue that ignorance is just as strong a position as being informed.  The long term effect of that sort of face-saving is accumulated mediocrity.  You have to be wrong to learn, and you have to learn to do good work.",
